{"tid":1021491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔怕貴、最怕飲唔到！】間間有錢賺！喜茶要攻陷香港","createTime":"2019-02-14T09:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T10:24:54.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"25dc32b74dd7b7ddd837ca9da4471a24350a6dfd","tid":1021491,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:39:36.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】近年不少人氣茶飲店登陸本港，雖然競爭激烈、成本高，但公司負責人表示，仍無損盈利能力。<br />\n<br />\n一條數十人的人龍，出現在一家內地飲品品牌門外，這個品牌在中港兩地最大分別是售價，同一款飲品，計及匯率因素，香港售價較內地貴30%至40%，個別飲品每杯索價近50元。<br />\n<br />\n香港茶飲店愈開愈多，市場競爭激烈之餘，成本亦甚高，但仍無損盈利能力。<br />\n<br />\n以這個品牌為例，每家分店平均每日售出逾2000杯茶，以平均每杯35元計，每月營業額逾200萬元。<br />\n<br />\n近年不少餐飲企業來港上市，公司指暫時未有相關計劃公布，但任何事情都有可能。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=337568\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D337568&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=9e440b1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D337568&h=939a674a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=337568</a>"},{"pid":"cea9825819e5e5ff1fd0873608acf5bc696aec7a","tid":1021491,"uid":4942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:41:19.000Z","msg":"成班港豬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"174f8462ad4bbaf17fdae691811fe3d55287a216","tid":1021491,"uid":24443,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"50杯 你飲撚埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca8be79a003291134dff2bf72952269dd0fb5e1","tid":1021491,"uid":69008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"174f8462ad4bbaf17fdae691811fe3d55287a216","tid":1021491,"uid":24443,"like":3